gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Cavaliers 105, Raptors 102
gameRecap.excerpt: The Cavaliers defeated the Raptors, 105-102. Darius Garland recorded 24 points, eight assists, and two rebounds for the Cavaliers, with Max Strus adding 20 points (all in the 3rd quarter) and 11 rebounds in the victory. Jakob Poeltl tallied 18 points and 13 rebounds for the Raptors in the defeat. The Cavaliers improve to 9-8 in the regular season, while the Raptors fall to 8-9.
